What everyone and their mother is asking



Ingredients & Safety (8)





Can I safely use Clorox® Regular-Bleach around children, pets and pregnant women?

Can I safely use Clorox® Regular-Bleach around children, pets and pregnant women?
Clorox's answer:


Yes. Used as directed, Clorox® Regular-Bleach shouldn’t pose hazards to your pets, children or pregnant women. In general, it's a good idea to remove pets and children from an area when cleaning it and to follow label precautionary instructions. When out of use, as with many household cleaners, you should keep it out of the reach of children and pets.
Still seeking answers? Ask away 




Is it safe to mix Clorox® Regular-Bleach with other household cleaning products?

Is it safe to mix Clorox® Regular-Bleach with other household cleaning products?
Clorox's answer:


No. We don’t recommend mixing Clorox® Regular-Bleach with other household chemicals, since toxic fumes could result.
Still seeking answers? Ask away 




Is Clorox® Regular-Bleach safe for septic systems?

Is Clorox® Regular-Bleach safe for septic systems?
Clorox's answer:


Yes. When used as directed, Clorox® Regular-Bleach is safe to use in septic systems. The bleach breaks down rapidly to mostly salt and water.
Still seeking answers? Ask away 




Can I use Clorox® Regular-Bleach to gargle, brush my teeth or clean cuts and scrapes?

Can I use Clorox® Regular-Bleach to gargle, brush my teeth or clean cuts and scrapes?
Clorox's answer:


No. Clorox® Regular-Bleach is not for personal usage.
Still seeking answers? Ask away 




Is Clorox® Regular-Bleach flammable?

Is Clorox® Regular-Bleach flammable?
Clorox's answer:


No, Clorox® Regular-Bleach is 90% water and is not flammable.
Still seeking answers? Ask away 




What is the shelf life of Clorox® Regular-Bleach?

What is the shelf life of Clorox® Regular-Bleach?
Clorox's answer:


Clorox® Regular-Bleach should be replaced every year and stored as directed for optimum performance.
Still seeking answers? Ask away 




What organisms does Clorox® Regular-Bleach kill?

What organisms does Clorox® Regular-Bleach kill?
Clorox's answer:


Laundry Sanitization (½ cup in a regular load or "max line" in an HE machineKlebsiella pneumoniaeMethicillin Resistant Staphylococcus aureus (MRSA)Pseudomonas aeruginosaStaphylococcus aureus
